How It Works | Revolar




























































0



















Home /
How It Works














Click to Communicate

Our communication gadgets are the fastest, most discreet way to reach trusted contacts with important info. Just click to send different custom text messages that include your GPS location.













Check-in or Get Support
 

While other safety devices are designed with only emergency alerts, our communication gadgets are customizable, so you can use the different alerts to get exactly the level of help you need.



 






Make Staying in Touch Simple >>



Watch How It Works


 








Communicate Faster When It Matters >>



Share Your Location With Contacts


If and When You Choose
 When you activate a Revolar Alert, your contact receives your message along with a Google Maps link that shows your location as you move. To stop sharing your location, just enter your custom PIN code in the Revolar App. Your contacts don’t need the Revolar App to receive alerts via text message and email.




 
















Wear It Anywhere
 

Clip your Revolar beneath your clothes or carry it on your keys



 





























Clicking Your Revolar
 

Discover how good it feels to have your loved ones by your side. 



 






Shop Revolar






























Setting Up Your Revolar

Download the Free Revolar App
Sync your Revolar to your phone
Add your 5 contacts





Revolar uses Bluetooth® low energy, which conserves battery life much better than other types of Bluetooth.














