Revolar Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
























revolar inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Security Services
Revolar Inc. provides a personal security wearable device. Its device allows the users to send an emergency alert message with location information by pressing a button on Revolar device to each person on the emergency contact list in case they are ever attacked or feel threatened.




Corporate Information
Address:

50 S Steele St Suite 250
Denver, CO, 80209
Denver, CO
United States


Phone:
