Careable technology.









Revolar is a wearable safety device that connects to an app on your phone through Low Energy Bluetooth®. Load up to 5 contacts in the Revolar app, and if you ever feel unsafe or are in a situation where you need help (allergic reaction, sexual assault, falling, etc.), simply press your Revolar button, and an alert with your GPS location will be sent to your contacts. From there, they are instructed to call you and/or get in touch with professional help on your behalf.

